atabase is currently only accessible during public hours at the main museum location in Palo Alto. The Museum of American Heritage is currently open to the public in the Williams House on Homer Ave. in Palo Alto. This house was custom built in 1907 by Dr. Thomas Williams for his residence and private medical practice.\"\n"}</information>
